INSERT INTO bsi_news_posts VALUES ('33', '1', 'What to See and Do in Rabac', 'Šta vidjeti i raditi u Rapcu', 'What to See and Do in Rabac', 'What to See and Do in Rabac', '<p>\r\n	Most visitors that come to Rabac are content to spend their holidays simply lying by the beach and enjoying the crystal clear, refreshing Adriatic. And we don&rsquo;t blame them, since these are our favorite pastimes as well.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Still, if you prefer a little more action, there are many options available. Snorkeling is another of our favorite activities, and if you come unprepared, many shops in Rabac offer affordable equipment, including masks, snorkels, and fins. You can spend hours lazily drifting in and out of the numerous and secluded coves as you watch passing schools of fish.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	If you prefer eating them, there are many good fishing spots to make your own catch. Or if you would rather have someone do it for you, you can enjoy a fun day on one of the Fish Picnic boats. Enjoy a short boat ride to the nearby island of Cres and a tasty fish lunch.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Other boat rentals and water sports can also be found along the harbor. Be sure to ask us for suggestions.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	For a break from the sea, you can explore the land and the many hiking trails up and along the coast. For more exertion, try the hike from Rabac up to Labin. It promises amazing views at the top.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	In the evening, enjoy a lovely stroll along the harbor. The boardwalk stretches for miles. You can dine at one of the many seafood restaurants, do a bit of shopping, or sip a glass of Croatian wine while watching the sea. Local music and entertainment is also often at hand.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The apartments can accommodate up to a maximum of 45 guests &ndash; perfect for family reunions, retreats or other group events.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Please inquire on our group reservations page about special rates for reserving the building as a whole.</p>', '<p>\r\n	Vecina posjetitelja koji dolaze u Rabac se sadržaj provesti svoj odmor jednostavno leži uz plažu i uživanje u kristalno jasnim, osvježavajuce Jadrana. I mi ih ne kriviti, jer su to na&scaron;e omiljene razonode kao dobro.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Ipak, ako želite malo vi&scaron;e akcije, postoje mnoge opcije na raspolaganju. Snorkeling je jo&scaron; jedan od na&scaron;ih omiljenih aktivnosti, i ako ste do&scaron;li nepripremljeni, mnoge trgovine u Rapcu ponudi pristupacne opreme, ukljucujuci i maske, disalice, peraja i. Možete provesti sate lijeno pluta u i iz brojnih i osamljenih uvala kao gledati dono&scaron;enje jata riba.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Ako vam je draže da ih jede, ima mnogo dobrih mjesta za ribolov napraviti svoj vlastiti ulov. Ili, ako biste radije imati netko to uciniti za vas, možete uživati u dan zabava na jednom od Fish Picnic brodova. Uživajte u kratkom vožnjom brodom do obližnjih otoka Cresa i ukusna riba rucak.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Ostalo Plovila i sportove na vodi mogu se naci duž luke. Budite sigurni da nas pitati za prijedloge.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Za predah od mora, možete istražiti zemlju i mnoge pje&scaron;acke staze i duž obale. Za vi&scaron;e napora, poku&scaron;ajte pje&scaron;acenje od Rapca do Labina. Ona obecava zadivljujuci pogled na vrhu.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	U vecernjim satima, uživajte lijep &scaron;etnje uz luku. riva proteže za milja. Možete rucati u jednom od brojni riblji restorani, napraviti malo shopping, ili pijuckati ca&scaron;u vina hrvatskih dok gledate more. Lokalni glazbe i zabave su takoder cesto na dohvat ruke.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	apartmani može ugostiti do najvi&scaron;e 45 gostiju - savr&scaron;en za obitelj reunions, vježbe ili druge grupe dogadaja.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Molimo raspitajte se o na&scaron;oj grupi rezervacije stranica o posebnim cijenama za rezervaciju zgrade kao cjeline.</p>', '<p>\r\n	Most visitors that come to Rabac are content to spend their holidays simply lying by the beach and enjoying the crystal clear, refreshing Adriatic. And we don&rsquo;t blame them, since these are our favorite pastimes as well.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Still, if you prefer a little more action, there are many options available. Snorkeling is another of our favorite activities, and if you come unprepared, many shops in Rabac offer affordable equipment, including masks, snorkels, and fins. You can spend hours lazily drifting in and out of the numerous and secluded coves as you watch passing schools of fish.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	If you prefer eating them, there are many good fishing spots to make your own catch. Or if you would rather have someone do it for you, you can enjoy a fun day on one of the Fish Picnic boats. Enjoy a short boat ride to the nearby island of Cres and a tasty fish lunch.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Other boat rentals and water sports can also be found along the harbor. Be sure to ask us for suggestions.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	For a break from the sea, you can explore the land and the many hiking trails up and along the coast. For more exertion, try the hike from Rabac up to Labin. It promises amazing views at the top.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	In the evening, enjoy a lovely stroll along the harbor. The boardwalk stretches for miles. You can dine at one of the many seafood restaurants, do a bit of shopping, or sip a glass of Croatian wine while watching the sea. Local music and entertainment is also often at hand.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The apartments can accommodate up to a maximum of 45 guests &ndash; perfect for family reunions, retreats or other group events.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Please inquire on our group reservations page about special rates for reserving the building as a whole.</p>', '<p>\r\n	Most visitors that come to Rabac are content to spend their holidays simply lying by the beach and enjoying the crystal clear, refreshing Adriatic. And we don&rsquo;t blame them, since these are our favorite pastimes as well.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Still, if you prefer a little more action, there are many options available. Snorkeling is another of our favorite activities, and if you come unprepared, many shop