, 23.08, 30.08.2011<br />\r\n						Labin<br />\r\n						<p>\r\n							Night Tour of Old Town Labin</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							Learn the history of the old town of Labin through legends, tales and events with professional guides who speak English. Meet us at the Tourist Info Desk in old town Labin at 9:30 pm for the sightseeing tour. The tour will conclude at 11 pm in grand fashion with homemade beverages and lit torches!</p>\r\n						<hr />\r\n						<h2>\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.istra.hr/en/regions_and_towns/town_and_cities/ltz_labin_rabac/events/6544-ch-0?&amp;l_over=1\"><strong>Labinske Konti</strong></a></h2>\r\n						30.07.2011<br />\r\n						Labin, Dubrova<br />\r\n						<p>\r\n							Traditional folklore event of the autochthonous Labin folklore</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							This festival offers traditional Istrian folk music and dance. Folk singers and dancers in costumes will entertain you with their beautifully sounding instruments and wonderful dancing.</p>\r\n						<hr />\r\n						<h2>\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.istra.hr/en/regions_and_towns/town_and_cities/ltz_labin_rabac/events/6545-ch-0?&amp;l_over=1\"><strong>Dubrova - Mediterranean Sculptors&#39; Symposium</strong></a></h2>\r\n						02.08.2011 - 13.09.2011<br />\r\n						Labin, Dubrova<br />\r\n						<p>\r\n							38th International symposium</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							Come join as we watch some of the most talented sculptors chisel away at rough stones that soon become beautiful shapes.</p>\r\n						<hr />\r\n						<h2>\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.istra.hr/en/regions_and_towns/town_and_cities/ltz_labin_rabac/events/6546-ch-0?&amp;l_over=1\"><strong>Fiat Bertone x 1/9 Croatia Tour</strong></a></h2>\r\n						10.09.2011 - 11.09.2011<br />\r\n						Rabac<br />\r\n						<p>\r\n							Oldtimer meeting</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							If you love cars, and really love the fiat, then you will not want to miss this event. Anyone who owns a fiat will be displaying their vehicle on the Rabac riva for this 