nter of Rabac along the entire coastline. This is a rocky beach that sits within the vicinity of the Valamar Sanfior, Pollux and Marina hotels. The natural shade of scented pines offers excellent protection for those wishing to escape the sun.</p>\r\n						<hr />\r\n						<h2>\r\n							<strong>Lanterna Beach</strong></h2>\r\n						<p>\r\n							Only 50 meters away from the Lanterna Apartments, the Lanterna beach is ideal for people who love to swim. The beach is close to the popular shops and food stands, where you can buy a beer to sip on while you look out onto the sea. Jet Skis and other fun water toys are available nearby as well.</p>\r\n						<hr />\r\n						<h2>\r\n							<strong>Maslinica Beach</strong></h2>\r\n						<p>\r\n							This beach is perfectly accessible for anyone, including those with disabilities. Maslinica has become one of the most popular beaches in Rabac because of the smooth stones that line the beach. You can rest comfortably here. Near the beach are shops, restaurants, bars, and ice cream stands to satisfy your cravings. You will also find a fun water slide and trampoline in the water that anyone can use. This beach can become crowded so make sure you arrive early.</p>\r\n						<hr />\r\n						<h3>\r\n							<span style=\"color:#0000cd;\"><strong>*Blue Flag Beaches</strong></span></h3>\r\n						<p>\r\n							Each of the above beaches is considered a Blue Flag beach. The Blue Flag is an exclusive eco-label award given to beaches and marinas that meet strict criteria for both water quality and environmental management. It was introduced in 1987, and sets common standards of good management across Europe.</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n<!-- end of main -->	</div>\r\n</div>', null, null, null, null, null, '0');
INSERT INTO bsi_site_contents VALUES ('79', 'Rabac Shopping', 'Rabac Shopping', 'Rabac Shopping', 'Rabac Shopping', 'N', '', '', '40', '5', '<div class=\"page_inside clear\">\r\n	<div class=\"subpage clear\">\r\n<!-- MAIN -->		<div class=\"clear fullwidth_pad\" id=\"main\">\r\n			<div class=\"boxes lines_x0x0x\">\r\n				<div class=\"container clear\">\r\n					<div class=\"inner\">\r\n						<div id=\"location_submenu\">\r\n							<div class=\"links\">\r\n								<ul>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<a href=\"page.php?id=40\">Restaurants</a></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<a href=\"page.php?id=76\">Excursions</a></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<a href=\"page.php?id=77\">Events</a></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<a href=\"page.php?id=78\">Beaches</a></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<a href=\"page.php?id=79\">Shopping</a></li>\r\n									<li>\r\n										<a href=\"page.php?id=80\">Nightlife</a></li>\r\n								</ul>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<h1>\r\n							<strong>SHOPPING</strong></h1>\r\n						<p>\r\n							Rabac\'s riva (waterfront) is bustling in the summer months with tourists who have come to enjoy the beautiful weather and crystal clear Adriatic Sea. Along the riva there are many small gift shops selling beach toys, paintings, handcrafts, perfumes, and other odds and ends.</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							There are also shops that sell clothing, bathing suits, jewelry, sunglasses, shoes, and other locally produced handcrafts.</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							Guests of Rabac will find pastry shops, food stands with fruits and vegetables, and a large grocery store at the center of the riva. There is also a pharmacy with medical supplies next to the grocery store.</p>\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						<br />\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n<!-- end of main -->	</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"page_inside clear\">\r